artistName.k: Clearful Journal, Mindfulness Diary and Mental Health Inc.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Finding a moment to pause and reflect is made a bit more effortless with Clearful. The journaling app is full of thoughtful prompts across a variety of themes that help us find moments of gratitude, check in with our mental health, and more. The power of reflection is made even more accessible with the app’s insights and reviews, which give us a chance to understand our habits and synthesize our entries into meaningful takeaways.
This journaling app is full of thoughtful prompts to help us find moments to reflect, while giving us a chance to understand our habits and synthesise our entries into meaningful takeaways.

Cette app de journal intime regorge de suggestions pour vous aider à trouver du temps pour une introspection, pour mieux comprendre vos habitudes et pour synthétiser le tout de façon concise et pertinente.
This journaling app is full of thoughtful prompts to help us find moments to reflect, while giving us a chance to understand our habits and synthesize our entries into meaningful takeaways.
這款日記 App 是你探索內心世界的良伴。它提供的貼心提示能引導你進行深度反思，幫助你更瞭解自己的習慣，並將零散的想法轉化為有意義的人生收穫。
